extendedInfo.description: The CrossFit South Bay Android App allows you to reserve classes while on the go!  The app allows you to see class schedules, sign-up for classes, view the ongoing promotions, as well as access contact information for each of our locations. Optimize your time and maximize the convenience of reserving classes from your Android.Download this App today!Also be sure to check out our website at: http://www.crossfitsouthbay.com
